>\n個個都傻更更,<br />\n支共政權唔係想香港人變聰明變成熟,<br />\n反而係想香港人變蠢自私短視,<br />\n你睇得透咩, 睇唔順咩, 有能力未走囉唔送,<br />\n搵支那人代替你香港人is ok"},{"pid":"75e44aa9fddeee3ee7b9b0498fef99ac6360b6ab","tid":452079,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:47:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"98e219b874709c0df3354db398b1b2e5528b907e","tid":452079,"uid":49316,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:59:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人地反軍國主義又扯到去愛唔愛國，愛唔愛港，班本土港獨狗真好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">五毛JR</span><br />\n反軍國主義為名<br />\n轉移視線為實<br />\n中國同其他獨裁政權一樣<br />\n為左掩飾自己腐敗。不惜利用民族主義製造假想敵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中國利用民族主義製造假想敵另一回事，而家講緊反軍國主義</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食屎啦<br />\n<br />\n生癌五毛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4050a111cabc2a2481d8e83a27549511a4cf27fb","tid":452079,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:55:55.000Z","msg":"根本有無大屠殺都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果南京算係 大飢荒都係人為"},{"pid":"81ef787be9d97dc07632b77453cafe8d627ff3e7","tid":452079,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:00:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89f72b3a90bfe65fc6a24d46e87a97c13f2811ef","tid":452079,"uid":127447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:04:57.000Z","msg":"有得移民去加拿大仲攪攪震正仆街！！要搞屎棍返支那啦！！！"}]}